name: Floral fancy
description:
Super cute X Small satchels are finally here! Same size as the Frejj clutch purse, with the added long adjustable strap. A practical little bag that you'll soon make your favourite. 

This X Small Satchel is fully lined in spotted fabric with a zippered suede pocket and 2 open suede pockets, adjustable strap in durable webbing with leather and closes with turn buttons.

name: Light in my life
description:
This style is fast becoming a favourite amongst FREJJ fans thats for sure! 
With a slight retro feel on a super modern carry all, this bag will certainly carry everything you need to and more! Just the right size for an overnight trip, for carry on luggage or for a day out shopping, this bag is versatile and practical.

Made from individual combo's of leather, the overnighter features the an outer pocket and leather shoulder straps. Inside is fully lined with a black water resistant fabric with suede pockets both open and zippered.

The dimensions are: 
Strap - 70cm 
Length- 37cm 
Width - 32 cm 
Depth - 15cm 
Zipper length - 60cm 
Front pocket - 19cm x 32cm

name: Friday's flowers
description:
Frejj's new style Tote with different coloured sides are fantastic for those days when you can't make up your mind. Each side has a different colour combination and is made from all leather. Bright and funky colour leather combo's are a unique feature of these beautiful FREJJ designs.

Like all Frejj products, the Tote is fully lined with a black water resistant cotton lining. The inside has a large open section with a zippered and small phone pocket on one side and two open pockets on the other, all in a super soft black suede.

Dimensions 
H-36.5cm 
W-33.5cm 
D-8cm 
Strap length - approx 65 cm

name: Summer clouds
description:
This is the medium size in my satchel range, a great size when you don't want to carry to much but still need to carry all the essentials. Inside is fully lined with black/grey  cotton lining. There is a main section, a zippered pocket and an open pocket on the inside front. Both pockets are in suede as is the backing of the front flap.

In all my bags I use industrial strength zippers and super strong magnetic clips. I also use heavy duty nickel slides and seatbelt webbing for the straps. The straps are fully adjustable and so strong, you need never worry that it will break under a heavy load.

W - 19cm
D - 8cm

name: " Triangles have landed "
description:
Incredible combination of Patent leather Blue underneath with a multi coloured striped back and front. Stitched on the front are brightly coloured leather triangles.

This is the medium size in my satchel range, a great size when you don't want to carry to much but still need to carry all the essentials. In side is fully lined with black and white spotted cotton lining. There is a main section, a zippered pocket and an open pocket on the inside front. Both pockets are in suede as is the backing of the front flap.

In all my bags I use industrial strength zippers and super strong magnetic clips. I also use heavy duty nickel slides and seatbelt webbing for the straps. The straps are fully adjustable and so strong, you need never worry that it will break under a heavy load.

The dimensions are as follows: 
H- 23cm 
W- 19cm 
D- 7cm
